description: Selina had a pretty sweet upbringing, with a mother who made any occasion extra special with every cake she baked. Now Selina is carrying along the delicious tradition by taking her mother’s dessert recipes through the streets of Dallas and Mesquite.In her mobile bakery, Selina and her talented team whip up cupcakes, pies, cake pops, and custom cakes, all baked from scratch with premium ingredients. These beautiful and tasty treats are perfect for any event; birthdays, weddings, or just great backyard shindigs. Pretty much all celebrations call for a dessert from Sweets by Selina.
name: Sweets by Selina
